"wixui-rich-text__text">&Phi;&omega;&tau;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;ά&phi;&iota;&sigma;&epsilon; &tau;&omicron; ό&rho;&alpha;&mu;ά &sigma;&omicron;&upsilon; &mu;&epsilon; &epsilon;&pi;&alpha;&gamma;&gamma;&epsilon;&lambda;&mu;&alpha;&tau;&iota;&sigma;&mu;ό &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &epsilon;&upsilon;&kappa;&omicron;&lambda;ί&alpha;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></h2></div><div id="comp-m4jrxvis" class="ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-m4jrxvis wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&Tau;&omicron; Studio R1 &epsilon;ί&nu;&alpha;&iota; &tau;&omicron; &nu;έ&omicron;, &upsilon;&pi;&epsilon;&rho;&sigma;ύ&gamma;&chi;&rho;&omicron;&nu;&omicron; &sigma;&tau;&omicron;ύ&nu;&tau;&iota;&omicron; &epsilon;&pi;&alpha;&gamma;&gamma;&epsilon;&lambda;&mu;&alpha;&tau;&iota;&kappa;ή&sigmaf; &phi;&omega;&tau;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;ά&phi;&iota;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; Retina Studios, &sigma;&tau;&rho;&alpha;&tau;&eta;&gamma;&iota;&kappa;ά &tau;&omicron;&pi;&omicron;&theta;&epsilon;&tau;&eta;&mu;έ&nu;&omicron; &sigma;&tau;&eta;&nu; &kappa;&alpha;&rho;&delta;&iota;ά &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &Delta;&rho;ά&mu;&alpha;&sigmaf;. &Sigma;&tau;ό&chi;&omicron;&sigmaf; &mu;&alpha;&sigmaf; &epsilon;ί&nu;&alpha;&iota; &nu;&alpha; &pi;&alpha;&rho;έ&chi;&omicron;&upsilon;&mu;&epsilon; &sigma;&epsilon; &kappa;ά&theta;&epsilon; &phi;&omega;&tau;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;ά&phi;&omicron; ό&lambda;&alpha; ό&sigma;&alpha; &chi;&rho;&epsilon;&iota;ά&zeta;&epsilon;&tau;&alpha;&iota; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &nu;&alpha; &pi;&rho;&alpha;&gamma;&mu;&alpha;&tau;&omicron;&pi;&omicron;&iota;ή&sigma;&epsilon;&iota; &tau;&eta;&nu; &iota;&delta;&alpha;&nu;&iota;&kappa;ή &sigma;&tau;&omicron;ύ&nu;&tau;&iota;&omicron; &phi;&omega;&tau;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;ά&phi;&iota;&sigma;&eta;, &chi;&omega;&rho;ί&sigmaf; &nu;&alpha; &alpha;&pi;&alpha;&iota;&tau;&epsilon;ί&tau;&alpha;&iota; &eta; &alpha;&gamma;&omicron;&rho;ά &alpha;&kappa;&rho;&iota;&beta;&omicron;ύ &epsilon;&xi;&omicron;&pi;&lambda;&iota;&sigma;&mu;&omicron;ύ ή &eta; &alpha;&nu;&alpha;&zeta;ή&tau;&eta;&sigma;&eta; &tau;&omicron;&upsilon; &kappa;&alpha;&tau;ά&lambda;&lambda;&eta;&lambda;&omicron;&upsilon; &chi;ώ&rho;&omicron;&upsilon;. &Sigma;&tau;&omicron; Studio R1, &theta;&alpha; &beta;&rho;&epsilon;ί&tau;&epsilon; ό&lambda;&alpha; &tau;&alpha; &alpha;&pi;&alpha;&rho;&alpha;ί&tau;&eta;&tau;&alpha; &epsilon;&rho;&gamma;&alpha;&lambda;&epsilon;ί&alpha; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &epsilon;&gamma;&kappa;&alpha;&tau;&alpha;&sigma;&tau;ά&sigma;&epsilon;&iota;&sigmaf; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &nu;&alpha; &delta;&eta;&mu;&iota;&omicron;&upsilon;&rho;&gamma;ή&sigma;&epsilon;&tau;&epsilon; &tau;&omicron; &alpha;&pi;&omicron;&tau;έ&lambda;&epsilon;&sigma;&mu;&alpha; &pi;&omicron;&upsilon; &epsilon;&pi;&iota;&theta;&upsilon;&mu;&epsilon;ί&tau;&epsilon;.</span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&Epsilon;&pi;&iota;&pi;&lambda;έ&omicron;&nu;, &eta; &omicron;&mu;ά&delta;&alpha; &mu;&alpha;&sigmaf; &epsilon;ί&nu;&alpha;&iota; &pi;ά&nu;&tau;&alpha; έ&tau;&omicron;&iota;&mu;&eta; &nu;&alpha; &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf; &upsilon;&pi;&omicron;&sigma;&tau;&eta;&rho;ί&xi;&epsilon;&iota;, &epsilon;ί&tau;&epsilon; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &tau;&eta;&nu; &epsilon;&gamma;&kappa;&alpha;&tau;ά&sigma;&tau;&alpha;&sigma;&eta; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &tau;&omicron; &sigma;&tau;ή&sigma;&iota;&mu;&omicron; &tau;&omicron;&upsilon; &epsilon;&xi;&omicron;&pi;&lambda;&iota;&sigma;&mu;&omicron;ύ, &epsilon;ί&tau;&epsilon; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &tau;&eta; &sigma;&omega;&sigma;&tau;ή &chi;&rho;ή&sigma;&eta; &tau;&omega;&nu; &epsilon;&rho;&gamma;&alpha;&lambda;&epsilon;ί&omega;&nu; &mu;&alpha;&sigmaf;. &Pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&phi;έ&rho;&omicron;&upsilon;&mu;&epsilon; &epsilon;&pi;ί&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; &epsilon;&kappa;&pi;&alpha;&iota;&delta;&epsilon;&upsilon;&tau;&iota;&kappa;ά &sigma;&epsilon;&mu;&iota;&nu;ά&rho;&iota;&alpha; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; ό&sigma;&omicron;&upsilon;&sigmaf; &epsilon;&pi;&iota;&theta;&upsilon;&mu;&omicron;ύ&nu; &nu;&alpha; &epsilon;&mu;&beta;&alpha;&theta;ύ&nu;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu; &sigma;&tau;&eta; &sigma;&tau;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu;&tau;&iota;&alpha;&kappa;ή &phi;&omega;&tau;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;ά&phi;&iota;&sigma;&eta; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &nu;&alpha; &beta;&epsilon;&lambda;&tau;&iota;ώ&sigma;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu; &tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &delta;&epsilon;&xi;&iota;ό&tau;&eta;&tau;έ&sigmaf; &tau;&omicron;&upsilon;&sigmaf;.</span></span></p>

