<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&Tau;&omicron; podcast setup &mu;&alpha;&sigmaf; &upsilon;&pi;&omicron;&sigma;&tau;&eta;&rho;ί&zeta;&epsilon;&iota; &mu;έ&chi;&rho;&iota; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; 4 ά&tau;&omicron;&mu;&alpha;, &pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&phi;έ&rho;&omicron;&nu;&tau;&alpha;&sigmaf; 4 &mu;&iota;&kappa;&rho;ό&phi;&omega;&nu;&alpha;, 4 &zeta;&epsilon;&upsilon;&gamma;ά&rho;&iota;&alpha; &alpha;&kappa;&omicron;&upsilon;&sigma;&tau;&iota;&kappa;ώ&nu;, &kappa;&omicron;&nu;&sigma;ό&lambda;&alpha; ή&chi;&omicron;&upsilon; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &kappa;&alpha;&tau;&alpha;&gamma;&rho;&alpha;&phi;&iota;&kappa;ό, &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &nu;&alpha; &delta;&iota;&alpha;&sigma;&phi;&alpha;&lambda;ί&sigma;&epsilon;&tau;&epsilon; &tau;&eta;&nu; ά&rho;&iota;&sigma;&tau;&eta; &pi;&omicron;&iota;ό&tau;&eta;&tau;&alpha; ή&chi;&omicron;&upsilon; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &epsilon;&iota;&kappa;ό&nu;&alpha;&sigmaf; &sigma;&tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &pi;&alpha;&rho;&alpha;&gamma;&omega;&gamma;έ&sigmaf; &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf;.</span></span></span></p></div><div id="comp-m7ae2dl5" class="MazNVa comp-m7ae2dl5 wixui-image"><div data-testid="linkElement" class="j7pOnl"><img loading="lazy" sizes="600px" srcSet="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/dab716_a7127b518c7d464487ad8095a66ff0d3~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_600,h_400,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/_D5A6950-edit.jpg 1x, https://static.wixstatic.com/media/dab716_a7127b518c7d464487ad8095a66ff0d3~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_1200,h_800,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/_D5A6950-edit.jpg 2x" id="img_comp-m7ae2dl5" src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/dab716_a7127b518c7d464487ad8095a66ff0d3~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_600,h_400,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/_D5A6950-edit.jpg" alt="_D5A6950-edit