ext__text">&Sigma;&tau;&alpha;&theta;&mu;ό&sigmaf; &Sigma;ύ&nu;&delta;&epsilon;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; &Kappa;ά&mu;&epsilon;&rho;&alpha;&sigmaf; &mu;&epsilon; &Upsilon;&pi;&omicron;&lambda;&omicron;&gamma;&iota;&sigma;&tau;ή (Tethering)</span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&Omicron; &Sigma;&tau;&alpha;&theta;&mu;ό&sigmaf; &sigma;ύ&nu;&delta;&epsilon;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; &kappa;ά&mu;&epsilon;&rho;&alpha;&sigmaf; &mu;&epsilon; &upsilon;&pi;&omicron;&lambda;&omicron;&gamma;&iota;&sigma;&tau;ή &mu;έ&sigma;&omega; Tethering &pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&phi;έ&rho;&epsilon;&iota; &sigma;&tau;&omicron;&upsilon;&sigmaf; &phi;&omega;&tau;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;ά&phi;&omicron;&upsilon;&sigmaf; &tau;&eta; &delta;&upsilon;&nu;&alpha;&tau;ό&tau;&eta;&tau;&alpha; &nu;&alpha; &sigma;&upsilon;&nu;&delta;έ&sigma;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu; &tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &kappa;ά&mu;&epsilon;&rho;έ&sigmaf; &tau;&omicron;&upsilon;&sigmaf; &alpha;&pi;&epsilon;&upsilon;&theta;&epsilon;ί&alpha;&sigmaf; &mu;&epsilon; &tau;&omicron;&nu; &upsilon;&pi;&omicron;&lambda;&omicron;&gamma;&iota;&sigma;&tau;ή &gamma;&iota;&alpha; ά&mu;&epsilon;&sigma;&eta; &pi;&rho;&omicron;&beta;&omicron;&lambda;ή &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &epsilon;&pi;&epsilon;&xi;&epsilon;&rho;&gamma;&alpha;&sigma;ί&alpha; &tau;&omega;&nu; &epsilon;&iota;&kappa;ό&nu;&omega;&nu; &sigma;&epsilon; &pi;&rho;&alpha;&gamma;&mu;&alpha;&tau;&iota;&kappa;ό &chi;&rho;ό&nu;&omicron;, &delta;&iota;&alpha;&sigma;&phi;&alpha;&lambda;ί&zeta;&omicron;&nu;&tau;&alpha;&sigmaf; έ&tau;&sigma;&iota; &upsilon;&psi;&eta;&lambda;ό&tau;&epsilon;&rho;&eta; &pi;&omicron;&iota;ό&tau;&eta;&tau;&alpha; &epsilon;&iota;&kappa;ό&nu;&alpha;&sigmaf; &alpha;&pi;ό &tau;&eta;&nu; &alpha;&rho;&chi;ή &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &phi;&omega;&tau;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;ά&phi;&iota;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf;. &Sigma;&tau;&omicron; Studio R1, &omicron; &Sigma;&tau;&alpha;&theta;&mu;ό&sigmaf; &Sigma;ύ&nu;&delta;&epsilon;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; &Kappa;ά&mu;&epsilon;&rho;&alpha;&sigmaf; &mu;&epsilon; &Upsilon;&pi;&omicron;&lambda;&omicron;&gamma;&iota;&sigma;&tau;ή &mu;&alpha;&sigmaf; &epsilon;ί&nu;&alpha;&iota; &epsilon;&xi;&omicron;&pi;&lambda;&iota;&sigma;&mu;έ&nu;&omicron;&sigmaf; &mu;&epsilon;: </span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;">&nbsp;</p>

<ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px; font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg, sans-serif; color:rgb(0, 0, 0);">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&Kappa;&alpha;&lambda;ώ&delta;&iota;&alpha; &sigma;ύ&nu;&delta;&epsilon;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &kappa;ά&mu;&epsilon;&rho;&epsilon;&sigmaf; Canon, Sony, Nikon &kappa;&alpha;&iota; ά&lambda;&lambda;&epsilon;&sigmaf;.</span></span></span></p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
