<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&Sigma;&tau;&omicron; Studio R1, &pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&phi;έ&rho;&omicron;&upsilon;&mu;&epsilon; &mu;&iota;&alpha; &pi;&omicron;&iota;&kappa;&iota;&lambda;ί&alpha; &alpha;&pi;ό &mu;&omicron;&nu;&alpha;&delta;&iota;&kappa;ά &sigma;&tau;&omicron;&iota;&chi;&epsilon;ί&alpha; &nu;&tau;&epsilon;&kappa;ό&rho; &pi;&omicron;&upsilon; &theta;&alpha; &epsilon;&nu;&iota;&sigma;&chi;ύ&sigma;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu; &tau;&eta; &delta;&eta;&mu;&iota;&omicron;&upsilon;&rho;&gamma;&iota;&kappa;ό&tau;&eta;&tau;ά &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &theta;&alpha; &pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&delta;ώ&sigma;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu; &iota;&delta;&iota;&alpha;ί&tau;&epsilon;&rho;&omicron; &chi;&alpha;&rho;&alpha;&kappa;&tau;ή&rho;&alpha; &sigma;&tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &phi;&omega;&tau;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;&alpha;&phi;ί&epsilon;&sigmaf; &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf;. &Omicron;&iota; &delta;&upsilon;&nu;&alpha;&tau;ό&tau;&eta;&tau;&epsilon;&sigmaf; &pi;&epsilon;&rho;&iota;&lambda;&alpha;&mu;&beta;ά&nu;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu;: </span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;">&nbsp;</p>

<ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg, sans-serif; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:18px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&Alpha;&lambda;&upsilon;&sigma;ί&delta;&epsilon;&sigmaf; &sigma;&tau;&eta;&nu; &omicron;&rho;&omicron;&phi;ή: </span>&Delta;ύ&omicron; &alpha;&lambda;&upsilon;&sigma;ί&delta;&epsilon;&sigmaf; &tau;&omicron;&pi;&omicron;&theta;&epsilon;&tau;&eta;&mu;έ&nu;&epsilon;&sigmaf; &sigma;&tau;&eta;&nu; &omicron;&rho;&omicron;&phi;ή, &alpha;&pi;ό &tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &omicron;&pi;&omicron;ί&epsilon;&sigmaf; &mu;&pi;&omicron;&rho;&omicron;ύ&mu;&epsilon; &nu;&alpha; &kappa;&rho;&epsilon;&mu;ά&sigma;&omicron;&upsilon;&mu;&epsilon; &delta;&iota;ά&phi;&omicron;&rho;&alpha; &alpha;&nu;&tau;&iota;&kappa;&epsilon;ί&mu;&epsilon;&nu;&alpha;, ό&pi;&omega;&sigmaf; &kappa;&omicron;ύ&nu;&iota;&epsilon;&sigmaf;, &sigma;&tau;&epsilon;&phi;ά&nu;&iota;&alpha; ή &omicron;&pi;&omicron;&iota;&omicron;&delta;ή&pi;&omicron;&tau;&epsilon; ά&lambda;&lambda;&omicron; &sigma;&tau;&omicron;&iota;&chi;&epsilon;ί&omicron; &chi;&rho;&epsilon;&iota;ά&zeta;&epsilon;&sigma;&tau;&epsilon; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &nu;&alpha; &delta;&eta;&mu;&iota;&omicron;&upsilon;&rho;&gamma;ή&sigma;&epsilon;&tau;&epsilon; &tau;&eta; &sigma;&omega;&sigma;&tau;ή &alpha;&tau;&mu;ό&sigma;&phi;&alpha;&iota;&rho;&alpha;.</span></span></span></p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&Mu;&pi;&alpha;&nu;&iota;έ&rho;&alpha; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; milk baths: &Iota;&delta;&alpha;&nu;&iota;&kappa;ή &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &delta;&eta;&mu;&iota;&omicron;&upsilon;&rho;&gamma;&iota;&kappa;έ&sigmaf; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &epsilon;&nu;&tau;&upsilon;&pi;&omega;&sigma;&iota;&alpha;&kappa;έ&sigmaf; &lambda;ή&psi;&epsilon;&iota;&sigmaf;, &eta; &mu;&pi;&alpha;&nu;&iota;έ&rho;&alpha; &mu;&alpha;&sigmaf; &epsilon;ί&nu;&alpha;&iota; &delta;&iota;&alpha;&theta;έ&sigma;&iota;&mu;&eta; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; milk baths, &pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&phi;έ&rho;&omicron;&nu;&tau;&alpha;&sigmaf; &mu;&omicron;&nu;&alpha;&delta;&iota;&kappa;έ&sigmaf; &delta;&upsilon;&nu;&alpha;&tau;ό&tau;&eta;&tau;&epsilon;&sigmaf; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &pi;&omicron;&rho;&tau;&rho;έ&tau;&alpha; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &theta;&epsilon;&mu;&alpha;&tau;&iota;&kappa;έ&sigmaf; &phi;&omega;&tau;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;&alpha;&phi;ί&sigma;&epsilon;&iota;&sigmaf;.</span></span></span></p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&Pi;&iota;&sigma;ί&nu;&alpha; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; fashion photography: &Iota;&delta;&alpha;&nu;&iota;&kappa;ή &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &phi;&omega;&tau;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;&alpha;&phi;ί&sigma;&epsilon;&iota;&sigmaf; &mu;ό&delta;&alpha;&sigmaf;, &eta; &pi;&iota;&sigma;ί&nu;&alpha; &mu;&alpha;&sigmaf; &pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&phi;έ&rho;&epsilon;&iota; &tau;&omicron; &tau;έ&lambda;&epsilon;&iota;&omicron; &sigma;&kappa;&eta;&nu;&iota;&kappa;ό &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &epsilon;&nu;&tau;&upsilon;&pi;&omega;&sigma;&iota;&alpha;&kappa;έ&sigmaf; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &delta;&upsilon;&nu;&alpha;&mu;&iota;&kappa;έ&sigmaf; &epsilon;&iota;&kappa;ό&nu;&epsilon;&sigmaf;.</span></span></span></p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:proxima-n-w01-reg,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Disco ball: &Gamma;&iota;&alpha; &nu;&alpha; &pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&theta;έ&sigma;&epsilon;&tau;&epsilon; &mu;&iota;&alpha; &delta;ό&sigma;&eta; &lambda;ά&mu;&psi;&eta;&sigmaf; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &kappa;ί&nu;&eta;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; &sigma;&tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &lambda;ή&psi;&epsilon;&iota;&sigmaf; &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf;, &eta; disco ball &epsilon;ί&nu;&alpha;&iota; &eta; &iota;&delta;&alpha;&nu;&iota;&kappa;ή &epsilon;&pi;&iota;&lambda;&omicron;&gamma;ή, &delta;&eta;&mu;&iota;&omicron;&upsilon;&rho;&gamma;ώ&nu;&tau;&alpha;&sigmaf; &mu;&omicron;&nu;&alpha;&delta;&iota;&kappa;ή &alpha;&tau;&mu;ό&sigma;&phi;&alpha;&iota;&rho;&alpha; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; έ&nu;&tau;&omicron;&nu;&alpha; &pi;&alpha;&iota;&chi;&nu;ί&delta;&iota;&alpha; &phi;&omega;&tau;ό&sigmaf;.</span></span></span></p>
</li>
